<p class="has-small-font-size">Sun, W., P. Bocchini, and B. D. Davison (2020), Applications of artificial intelligence for disaster management, <em>Nat. Hazards</em>, <em>103</em>, 2,631–2,689, <a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/s11069-020-04124-3" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">https://doi.org/10.1007/s11069-020-04124-3</a>.</p>

